{"tid":1748742,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[數據分析] 原來泛民本土可以輕鬆贏350席！保皇狗4份1都攞唔到！但因為一個原因做唔到......","createTime":"2019-11-23T21:35:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-24T09:33:27.000Z","uid":470,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0af3d70c1dc17a8fdb059868432ff7847485ed63","tid":1748742,"uid":470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T21:35:04.000Z","msg":"根據2016年立法會選舉各區票站統計<br />\n四百幾區<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">有超過350個區，泛民本土得票多過建制！</span></strong><br />\n區選贏到開巷，地區搶盡話語權，保皇狗無大水喉利益輸送變落水狗<br />\n仲可以立法會功能組別多兩席，選舉委員會多百幾票(雖然無乜用，但可以撚下共狗都開心)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但上屆只係相隔一年(2015)嘅區議會選舉，保皇狗贏左成300席！！！<br />\n點解立法會選舉同區議會選舉爭咁遠？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">係因為你同你啲friend無出去投票呀！！！！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n備註：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">1. 數據取自2016年立法會選舉結果，所以係以2016年嘅劃界計算<br />\n2. 部分票站跨區幫小票站點票，例如「大嶼山」係一個好撚大嘅選區，「大澳」屬於「大嶼山」但選票會運去東涌集中點算<br />\n3. 泛民建制歸類從嚴處理，部分歸類如下：<br />\n香港島：王維基 泛民 沈志超 建制<br />\n九龍西：李泳漢 狄志遠 建制 何志光 林依麗 唔計<br />\n九龍東：呂永基 泛民 譚香文 唔計<br />\n新界西：馮檢基 呂智恆 泛民 張慧晶 湯詠芝 唔計<br />\n新界東：鄭家富 泛民 方國珊 麥嘉晉 建制</span>"},{"pid":"5dd67ded579b0ba73da1456896b4701d8d9a9dd6","tid":1748742,"uid":470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T00:53:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0529bc931b93a9812d7944f88fa508146ac8fa2","tid":1748742,"uid":470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T06:44:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c53774af70a4fbb9be98b6ded9c4786c5fb046c","tid":1748742,"uid":251366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T07:25:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OYi14eE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOYi14eE.jpg&h=86022223&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"46777d0d0e6c6e13c50b0d4d94d0452e6238071f","tid":1748742,"uid":204306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T07:29:35.000Z","msg":"馮檢基 建制<br />\n何志光 白卡"},{"pid":"66a28666f9fa70ccafcddb01929d14bb599639c7","tid":1748742,"uid":272422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T07:34:33.000Z","msg":"唔好輕敵 出嚟投票啊"},{"pid":"302a5ae0e99814bc9472e6995fa11fd879b4e0dd","tid":1748742,"uid":470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"46777d0d0e6c6e13c50b0d4d94d0452e6238071f","tid":1748742,"uid":204306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T07:29:35.000Z","msg":"馮檢基 建制<br />\n何志光 白卡"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T09:33:27.000Z","msg":"2016年會投馮檢基嘅人應該係會投泛民"}]}